# Copy to .env.local (gitignored) for local tooling / future CLI automation only.
# Do not put real secrets in tracked files. Never use VITE_* prefix for API keys (inlined into the browser bundle).
#
# Docs: docs/TOOLCHAIN_ACCESS.md

# --- Google Gemini (local scripts: text, image understanding, image generation) ---
# https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/quickstart
# GEMINI_API_KEY=

# --- ElevenLabs (local scripts: TTS, SFX, music per key scopes) ---
# https://elevenlabs.io/docs/eleven-api/quickstart
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# --- Other optional vendors ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Optional: CI or deploy (example names only; configure in host UI, not here) ---
# DEPLOY_TOKEN=
